Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子呐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,91年的款式要130万！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太贵了 S13
